From 4fa26400782fea1b4e9eaa0f3297283ebde80c58 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: John Crispin <john@phrozen.org>
Date: Sat, 2 Aug 2025 06:47:35 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] mediatek: edgecore eap111 fixes

* add dual boot support
* add bootcount support
* add led support
* add macaddr support
* swap eth ports
* add edgecore_eap111_eeprom_dbdc.bin
* fix dts to allow cmdline

Signed-off-by: John Crispin <john@phrozen.org>
